spec_data.Name: nodejs-int64-buffer
spec_data.Description:
JavaScript's number based on IEEE-754 could only handle 53 bits precision. This
module provides a couple of classes: Int64BE and Uint64BE which could hold 64
bits long integer and loose no bit.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 03:04:33 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: 64bit Long Integer on Buffer/Array/ArrayBuffer in Pure JavaScript
